data.description: Your exclusive island lifestyle awaits! Create your own dream home on this quiet street, just blocks from the ocean and proximate to Sunset Park and neighborhood schools. Charming 1950's single-story ranch house features original beam ceilings and hardwood floors. French doors open to a Trex deck and stone terrace, designed for entertaining and relaxation. Significant price reduction reflects sellers' readiness to move as they have found a new home.
